name: The "You Coulda Done Better" Card
description: Valentine's Day is a day when couples celebrate their love. What better way to say "I love you endlessly, yet I know I am barely able to take care of myself and ruin just about everything I touch" than with this romantic card! It is printed in the USA with soy inks, on 100# recycled cover stock. It comes with a matching envelope. Limited run. Comes with a personal love note.

name: The "You Better Be A Human" Card
description: Lovely card for all those situations where you aren't quite sure if your friend is a cat or a human. The front says "This card is for a person." and the interior of the 5x7 folded card says "I hope for everyone's sake, you are not a cat" in a lovely Helvetica typeface. Printed on a 100# recycled cover stock, it is scored and folded to fit into the matching envelope, this card is perfect for Christmas, St. Patrick's Day, loved ones, reuinions, and other non-specific celebrations.

name: The "I Guess" Card
description: Lovely card for all those situations where you know you haven't quite nailed it. The front says "I got you something.," and the interior of the 5x7 folded card says "This is it, I guess." in a lovely Helvetica typeface.  Printed on a 100# recycled cover stock, it is scored and folded to fit into the matching envelope, this card is perfect for making someone's day.

name: The "Awkward Situation" Card
description: Lovely card for all those situations where there just isn't anything left to say. The front says "Well," and the interior of the 5x7 folded card says "this is awkward, huh?" in a lovely Helvetica typeface.  Printed on a 100# recycled cover stock, scored and folded to fit into the matching envelope, this card is perfect for gift giving of all occasions.

name: Super Cool 4 Pack
description: 1 each of the 4 cards offered, plus a blank envelope for each. Perfect for mailing to a loved one, handing to a friend, or giving to someone you generally dislike.
